{"tid":2313218,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[BNO佳音] 將容許太空人計劃, 父/母一方可留港工作","createTime":"2020-12-05T14:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T00:27:57.000Z","uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54eb834febf10db68195d28d844ab72d713237c0","tid":2313218,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201205/VETV6QBEHFHGBKLHEI2E524HAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201205%2FVETV6QBEHFHGBKLHEI2E524HAY%2F&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQo6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=21846c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201205%2FVETV6QBEHFHGBKLHEI2E524HAY%2F&h=ffd1b20d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201205/VETV6QBEHFHGBKLHEI2E524HAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n未有細節<br />\n<br />\nBNO留英計劃「5+1」方案於下月31日正式接受港人申請，大批港人向英國護照署續領已過期多年的BNO，單計今年10月，英方已向近6萬港人發出續期BNO，創單月歷史新高。《蘋果》從兩個消息證實，BNO計劃細節將有「佳音」，就是容許「太空人計劃」，打破英國移民政策要求申請人和受養人必須一同移居英國的規定，這安排可讓父或母一方可續留港工作，子女則留在英國讀書，最終一家可取得英國永久居留。"},{"pid":"6552a89587b27150a5875ac88ed692279432a130","tid":2313218,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T00:27:57.000Z","msg":"蘋果啲消息唔太可靠，聽住先"}]}